high_descs: Pick a mug from the refrigerator.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Place the mug in the sink and wash it with the tap water.
Take that cup and head to the coffeetable in the living room by turning around.
Place the mug on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Place the mug on the coffee table by washing it.

high_descs: Place yourself in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge. Take the mug. Close the fridge door.
Place the mug in the refrigerator. Open the faucet. Wait 5 seconds. Close the faucet. Take the mug.
Go to the coffeetable, place yourself between the sofa and the coffeetable. Stand in front of the coffeetable.
Place the mug on the far left side of the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Find a mug and place it on a coffee table.

high_descs: turn around and walk to the fridge.
open the refrigerator and take the mug out of it.
go to the sink and put the cup in the sink.
turn the water on and wash the mug.
take the cup and go to the coffeetable.
Put the mug down on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Get the mug and put it on the coffee table.
